<lb n="0390b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0390b1201">爾時金剛鈴明王。說自心明曰。</p>
<lb n="0390b13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0390b1301">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>健吒<note place="inline">一<anchor xml:id="beg_ac" type="star"/>句<anchor xml:id="end_ac"/></note>囉拏囉拏吽<note place="inline">引</note>發吒<note place="inline">半音二</note></p>
